data.description: Discover your dream home in Glennville! This spacious brick house offer the perfect blend of comfort and elegance. With 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, 1 half bath, a dining room, formal living room, family room and a bonus room, there's ample space for your family to grow and entertain. Cozy up by one of the two fireplaces on chilly evenings. Step outside into your own oasis - an inground pool along with a covered back patio and a privacy fence awaits you, making it a perfect spot for relaxation and fun. The property features a 2 car attached carport and a 1 car garage. This property sits on a sprawling 2.28 acres with a sprinkler system that once nurtured pecan trees. Now you can enjoy the bounty of an orange tree, fig and pear tree right in your backyard. But that's not all! There's an additional detached space that could serve as a studio apartment, ideal for guests or even potential rental income. It comes with a half bath that could be turned into a full bath and an attached one car-garage/workshop for convenience. An architectual roof was installed on all dwellings in Nov of 2020. This property is not just a home; it's a haven for family gatherings and outdoor entertainment. Contact me today to make this amazing property yours and live the life you've always imagined.
